r2387 | sam | 2002-08-25 11:40:00 +0200 (Sun, 25 Aug 2002) | 14 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/include/aout_internal.h
   M /trunk/include/vlc_symbols.h
   M /trunk/modules/audio_output/alsa.c
   M /trunk/modules/audio_output/arts.c
